HEADWORD: Pathan
<hw>Pathan</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A native or inhabitant of
Afghanistan, especially of the Pashtun tribes of southern
Afghanistan.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Afghan, Afghanistani, Pashto, pashtun.</syn>⟦br⟧
